kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=081b6ebd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果十月一我地再幫支共賀一賀佢，搞到全美國都知支共國慶我地用美國國歌慶祝，你話會激到維尼幾咁高興？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實就無話要等到十月一既，<br />\n黎緊每次發夢都可以唱！！！！<br />\n<br />\n但大佬大家真係要練一練佢<br />\n事關首歌音域廣、歌詞繞口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MV with Lyrics: </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=10800280\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">Oh, say can you see by the dawn's early light</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">What so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars through the perilous fight,</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">O'er the ramparts we watched were so gallantly streaming?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air,</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Gave proof through the night that our flag was still there.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh, say does that star-spangled banner yet wave</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?</span><br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1sKkdk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1sKkdk.gif&h=5c4ce310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, <br />\nthe Revolution of Our Times"},{"pid":"2e5b48c81a2580ff95520f39e0d81a0ee9158ccb","tid":1514964,"uid":20633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62338f60ea346605e8dfe1363c0a11b816ddb390","tid":1514964,"uid":20633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2674841c866bd15dd05216ee602b9f35c2f6cb","tid":1514964,"uid":20633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d1a6a8acaba3d7b7068f39446f2000ceda114e","tid":1514964,"uid":20633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8987e4b4dd1da3e76e5c83f7881713a1d1f5df72","tid":1514964,"uid":20633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmo